reviews.text: Historic place. Far more than stag and hen parties. Lots to visit with good restaurants and quaint pubs. Good for shopping too. Will go again.

Old style Victorian style station that has recently been refurbished there is a indoor part of the station upstairs with seating, toilets shops etc & platforms downstairs which are covered with roof but exposed to the elements, the station is also in the heart of the city centre & placed in a good location , the staff are also helpful

Very clean, helpful info desk ..
Got coop supermarket and costa cafe too
Classic railway station. Usually clean and tidy.
